The '''Bishop of Melanesia''' is the head of the [[Anglican]] [[Church of the Province of Melanesia]].

==List of holders==
#[[John Coleridge Patteson]], 1861-1871
#[[John Richardson Selwyn]], 1877-1892
#[[Cecil Wilson]], 1894-1911
#[[Cecil Wood]], 1911-1919
#[[John Manwaring Steward]], 1919-1928
#[[Frederick M. Molyneux]], 1928-1932
#[[Walter Hubert Baddeley]], 1932-1947
#[[S. G. Caulton]], 1947-1958
#[[Alfred Thomas Hill]], 1958-
